<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Palanquin' rel='stylesheet'>
    <style>
        .separator {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .separator::before, .separator::after {
            content: '';
            flex: 1;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(218, 218, 218);
        }

        .separator::before {
            margin-right: 13.25em;
        }

        .separator::after {
            margin-left: 13.25em;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
<div style="width: 100%;height: 97px;background-color:#ebedf4">
    <div style=" width: 29%;height: 97px;background-color:#25203e;float: left">
        <img style=" width: 100%;height: 97px;background-color:#25203e;"
             src="https://i.ibb.co/nwzLByM/lodopdf.png">
    </div>
    <div style="width: 100%;height: 97px;background-color:#ebedf4;">
        <div style="font-family: Palanquin;font-size: 26px;font-stretch: normal;font-style: normal;line-height: normal;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: center;color:#1c1e25;padding-top:20px">
            Plateforme CNB - e-Actes sous signature privée
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<br>
<div style="margin-left: 20px">
    <h3>De:</h3>
    <p style="font-family: Palanquin">{{ lastname }} {{ name }},</p>
    <hr style=" width: 34px;margin-left:0px;
  height: 2px;
  background-color: rgb(37, 35, 59);
">
    <p style="font-family: Palanquin">88 aveue des champs élysee, PARIS,78000</p>
    <br>
    <p style="font-family: Palanquin">Bonjour,</p>
    <p style="font-family: Palanquin"><a href="#">{{ email }}</a></p>
    <h3 style="font-family: Palanquin">Vous a envoyé le document signé électroniquement sur le plateforme e-Acte sous signature privée du CNB, veuillez cliquer sur le lien suivant :</h3>
    <div class="separator">
        <div style="text-align: center">
            <a style="display:inline-block; font-family: Palanquin;  width: 117px;
  height: 25px;
  background-color: #0279ff;color:white;border-radius:6px;"
               href="{{ host }}download-file?act={{ act }}&timestamp={{ timestamp }}">Connectez-vous</a>
        </div>

    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <p style="font-family: Palanquin">Cordialement</p>
    <div>
        <img style="width: 150px;" src="https://encyclopedie.avocats.fr/icon/LogoHome.png">
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
